Class LittleEndianSeekableBytesReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exceeddata.sdk.vdata.binary.LittleEndianSeekableBytesReader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BinarySeekableReader, Serializable

    public class LittleEndianSeekableBytesReader
extends Object
implements BinarySeekableReader
    A class for reading data bytes in Little-Endian format. The reader must be seekable.
